    Create free account
    <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8h10m0 0l-4-4m4 4l-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
